      <title>阿什莫尔反驳共识，押注中国而非印度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ashmore-counters-consensus-with-big-bet-on-china-over-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于伦敦的资产管理公司安石集团(Ashmore Group PLC)正在减少对印度股市的投资，并将中国股票列为其新兴市场基金的第一选择，该公司认为印度股市被过度炒作且过度拥挤，而中国股市则有望反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ashmore-counters-consensus-with-big-bet-on-china-over-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
